OL,3,CAgreement reached for 'dual use' of
OL,4,CRAF Scampton site
OL,6,FAn agreement in principle has been
OL,7,Freached to use a former RAF base
OL,8,Fearmarked as an asylum camp as a
OL,9,Fheritage centre as well.
OL,11,FIt comes after months of negotiations
OL,12,Fbetween the Home Office and West
OL,13,FLindsey District Council (WLDC) over
OL,14,Fthe future usage of the RAF Scampton
OL,15,Fsite in .
OL,17,FWLDC announced that they had agreed to
OL,18,Fexplore the temporary, dual use of the
OL,19,Fsite as both an asylum seeker
OL,20,Fprocessing camp and a heritage centre
OL,21,Fregeneration project.
