OL,3,CAgreement reached for 'dual use' of
OL,4,CRAF Scampton site
OL,6,FFollowing a Special Development Order
OL,7,F(SDO), the Home Office gained planning
OL,8,Fpermission to use the site as an
OL,9,Fasylum centre until October 2027.
OL,11,FHowever, the council will also now be
OL,12,Fallowed to use a portion of the land
OL,13,Fto pursue its #300 million
OL,14,Fregeneration of the site with its
OL,15,Fpartner, Scampton Holdings Ltd.
