OL,3,CAgreement reached for 'dual use' of
OL,4,CRAF Scampton site
OL,6,FThe government agency is reported to
OL,7,Fbe retaining just 10% of the site to
OL,8,Fhouse up to 800 migrants awaiting
OL,9,Fprocessing, a significant reduction
OL,10,Ffrom the original plan to accommodate
OL,11,F2,000.
OL,13,FScampton Councillor Roger Patterson
OL,14,Fcelebrated the "brilliant news",
OL,15,Fadding "it's what we've all been
OL,16,Fwanting."
OL,18,F"Our future is now secure. We have a
OL,19,Fbright future to look forward to, and
OL,20,Fit's absolutely brilliant for
OL,21,FLincolnshire."
