OL,6,FCouncillor Patterson also noted that
OL,7,Fthis is likely one of the biggest
OL,8,Finvestments in Lincolnshire.
OL,10,FAlthough he acknowledged that talks
OL,11,Fbetween the two parties had begun
OL,12,Fbefore Prime Minister Rishi Sunak
OL,13,Fcalled a General Election for 4 July,
OL,14,Fhe suspects that the positive step
OL,15,Fforward might be related to the
OL,16,Fupcoming election.
OL,18,FLocal resident and campaigner against
OL,19,Fthe Home Office plans, Rachael Green,
OL,20,Fwas more hesitant about the news due
OL,21,Fto the lack of detail.
