OL,6,FHowever, she insisted that it can only
OL,7,Fbe a good thing as long as the
OL,8,Fheritage assets on the site are
OL,9,Fprotected.
OL,11,F"If it means the heritage assets can
OL,12,Fbe protected, then it's only a good
OL,13,Fthing," she said.
