OL,3,CAgreement reached for 'dual use' of
OL,4,CRAF Scampton site
OL,6,FIn a letter, Gainsborough MP Sir
OL,7,FEdward Leigh (Conservative) explained:
OL,8,F"The agreement in principle includes a
OL,9,Fprovision that in October 2025 the
OL,10,FHome Office will begin to reduce the
OL,11,Faccommodation footprint of the site by
OL,12,Fremoving the modular accommodation on
OL,13,Fthe hangar apron, with WLDC looking to
OL,14,Foccupy that area in April 2026.
OL,16,F"The Home Office are working with
OL,17,FHistoric England and WLDC to put in
OL,18,Fplace a plan to maintain the heritage
OL,19,Fof the site for the future.
