OL,6,F"We believe this is a significant and
OL,7,Fpositive development for the local
OL,8,Fcommunity and I look forward to
OL,9,Fworking together with you as the
OL,10,Fregeneration plan moves forward.
OL,12,FWLDC leader Trevor Young (Liberal
OL,13,FDemocrat) added: "The specific details
OL,14,Fof the agreement are still being
OL,15,Ffinalised, but this paves the way
OL,16,Fforward for the short-term and long-
OL,17,Fterm use of the site.
