OL,6,F"The council have always been clear
OL,7,Fthat whilst it is our view that the
OL,8,Fsite is unsuitable for large scale
OL,9,Fasylum accommodation, protecting the
OL,10,Finvestment and regeneration plans for
OL,11,Fthe site is a priority.
OL,13,F"This agreement provides the
OL,14,Fprinciples by which we can collaborate
OL,15,Fto unlock our investment and
OL,16,Fregeneration plan by working with the
OL,17,FHome Office through a shared use
OL,18,Fproposal."
