OL,6,FSally Grindrod-Smith, Director of
OL,7,FPlanning, Regeneration and Communities
OL,8,Fat WLDC, also explained there is still
OL,9,Fa "huge amount of detail to work
OL,10,Fthrough."
OL,12,FShe said: "I am confident that over
OL,13,Fthe coming months we can continue to
OL,14,Fuse our energy and passion to protect
OL,15,Fthis site and to develop an innovative
OL,16,Fand creative shared use proposal which
OL,17,Fallows for the kickstarting of plans
OL,18,Fto bring significant investment into
OL,19,FWest Lindsey and Lincolnshire."
